link: https://app-twitt-explainer.herokuapp.com
app maked with flask, and a classifier SVM with 78% of accuracy. The interpretation results are guive by LIME Framework.
The app receive a english text about covid from tweet (without #,@) and classifier the sentiment with positive, neutral or negative and the black-box (SVM) is
explained with the words more relevants to classifier with LIME Framework. The app also run with text of sites about covid.

